Ollle Otto PRINCE, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 12773. United States Court of Appeals Fifth Circuit. March 20, 1950. *582No Appearance entered for Appellant. Frank B. Potter, U. S. Atty., Fort Worth, Tex., Clyde G. Hood, Asst. U. S. Atty., Dallas, Tex., for appellee.

Before HOLMES, McCORD, and BORAH, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The judgment appealed from is affirmed.
